, \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The email stated that Alonso's departure was both requested by the athlete and authorized by the Head of Mission.\", \"from\": 821, \"to\": 934, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She noted that Alonso's presence \\\"had created an inappropriate environment for the Paraguayan team.\\\"\", \"from\": 935, \"to\": 1035, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1018, \"end\": 1028, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay\", \"score\": 0.9499502158640624, \"rank\": 0.0526855852891702, \"text\": \"Paraguayan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alonso has since returned to Dallas, Texas, where she is currently pursuing higher education.\", \"from\": 1037, \"to\": 1130, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1066, \"end\": 1072, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dallas\", \"score\": 0.8898746411507235, \"rank\": 0.1229025768767941, \"text\": \"Dallas\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dallas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dallas\"}, {\"begin\": 1074, \"end\": 1079, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas_Longhorns\", \"score\": 0.6253384038599825, \"rank\": 0.5481703731438067, \"text\": \"Texas\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas_Longhorns\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas_Longhorns\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Addressing the situation on social media, the athlete denied being expelled against her will and refuted false claims, stating, \\\"I was never kicked out or expelled from anywhere, please stop spreading false information.\\\"\", \"from\": 1131, \"to\": 1351, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite her previous achievements, including three medals at the 2022 South American Rosario Youth Games, Alonso has indicated that swimming is not her ultimate career goal.\", \"from\": 1353, \"to\": 1526, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1429, \"end\": 1437, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999849293559365, \"rank\": 1.4288981737688935e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a recent interview, she expressed her emotional response to her final race, saying, \\\"I love swimming competitively, but that's not what I want for my life.\\\"\", \"from\": 1527, \"to\": 1686, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"COMMENTS  Comments are moderated and generally will be posted if they are on-topic and not abusive.\", \"from\": 1688, \"to\": 1787, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For more information, please see ourComments FAQ  This material may not be published, broadcast, rewritten,                     redistributed or derived from.\", \"from\": 1789, \"to\": 1947, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Unless otherwise stated, all content is                     copyrighted \\u00a9 2025 The Express Tribune.\", \"from\": 1948, \"to\": 2047, \"entities\": []}]}"